<cell id="cell-0"><cell_type>markdown</cell_type># Lab 3.5 — Chunking benchmark
Fixed vs recursive vs semantic vs structural on 100 arXiv abstracts.
Reuses 03-naive-rag/data/arxiv + eval_questions.json.
Cost: ~$0.12 (re-embed corpus 4x).</cell id="cell-0">
